headline: NTSB urges quick fix on Boeing plane engines to prevent smoke from filling cabin after a bird strike
summary: Safety experts recommended Wednesday that the engines on Boeing's troubled 737 Max airplanes be modified quickly to prevent smoke from filling the cockpit or cabin after a safety feature is activated...
